# Fowl Words вАФ scoring & awards

## Round flow
`word-selection` вЖТ `clue-submission` вЖТ `deduplication` вЖТ `reveal` вЖФ `guess` вЖТ `scored`

## How you win
- **Guesser:** guess the secret word within 4 attempts (timers 60s вЖТ 40s вЖТ 20s).
- **Givers:** earn when their clue is **visible** at a correct guess (USED).
- **Game:** highest cumulative score after all rounds.

## Points (server-authoritative вАФ clients display only)

| Source | Who | Points | When |
|--------|-----|--------|------|
| Correct guess | Guesser | 10 / 5 / 2 / 1 by attempt | Win |
| USED | Giver (visible clue) | Same as attempt | Win |
| FAST | Fastest visible submitters | +3 (+2, +1 at 6+ players) | Win |
| DUPLICATE | Giver in dup group | -1 | Any outcome |
| вЭ§пЄП Peer love | Giver вЖТ other clues | +1 per heart per author | **Win only**; reveal/guess |
| в≠Р Most Helpful | Guesser вЖТ one clue | `max(1, floor(5/N))` per co-author | Result; **win only** |
| рЯСО Boo | Giver or guesser | 0 | Givers: reveal/guess ¬Ј Guesser: result |

## Award rules (UI + backend must match)
- Givers: one optional вЭ§пЄП per other clue (toggle per card), one рЯСО per round; never own clue.
- Guesser sees live вЭ§пЄП/рЯСО counts while guessing (read-only).
- Peer love on visible duplicates is allowed (+1 like any visible clue).
- Boo never subtracts points. Votes show counts only, never voter names.
- Vocabulary: **Peer love / Most Helpful / Boo** вАФ never nod, shame, MVP, or star in copy.

## Source of truth
- Core round math: `functions/src/games/fowl-words/scoring.ts`
